{"tid":1492802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為任正非：對香港示威沒有意見 只關心機場要打開","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T01:25:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3d23abbc7b5bc000367d637292641f75107113","tid":1492802,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"中國電訊設備製造商華為始創人任正非表示，對香港的局勢沒有看法，只關心香港機場的路要打開，否則有人坐飛機去學校會有困難。華為心聲社區網站發布任正非今個月15日，接受英國天空電視專訪的紀要，任正非被問到對香港情況的看法時表示，除了關注香港機場的情況，並無其他想法，並提到中國還是非常穩定，穩定最大的基礎是改善窮人生活。<br />\n<br />\n任正非又提到，美國將華為46間子公司列入出口管制實體清單，是不太公平的決定，因為華無做錯事，而華為將設備換成自家研發的零部件後，設備效率比原來用美國零部件時提升了30%。"},{"pid":"fb168c0d74f924545aa5c183f347d0598fce4ca9","tid":1492802,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a877a8f6c4101fa84312dcab0c0207e352784d79","tid":1492802,"uid":259833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"Ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8c2f423137f13c9c112c9f217739adf832feca","tid":1492802,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102451cbb4ebf1419a5715a9ba5781ce2f1ba677","tid":1492802,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces